originalText.text: Please take this review seriously and take your money elsewhere. We placed an order here back in JULY with a down payment. It is now NOVEMBER and we have been given the run around for months. Don't waste your time. Also when I called to inquire, the owner hung up on me. So i'm guessing we'll have to take this to court. Spare yourself the trouble and don't do business with these people.

originalText.text:
One star only because there was nothing lower. Left my item for almost two weeks just to have patches sown on it. Abraham the tailor even took pics of how I wanted things done. Went away on vacation and came back thinking it would be complete. His reply (finally!) to my text was to request pictures (which he already had and took with his own camera.)
I summarily went and retrieved my jacket. Will not only never set foot in there again. Won’t even walk on that side of 116th street.
